  --body "$(cat <<'EOF'
## Summary

The p24p compiler enters an apparent infinite loop when compiling Pascal programs that combine 12+ user-defined procedures with a main block exceeding ~14 statements. The compiler runs billions of instructions with no output, never producing "; OK" or any error.

## Reproduction

Take this working 147-line program (compiles at ~39M instructions):

```pascal
